quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,46,"Àti ìjọ Nūh tí ó ṣíwájú (wọn), dájúdájú wọ́n jẹ́ ìjọ arúfin."
  51,47,"Àti pé sánmọ̀, A mọ ọ́n (sí òkè yín) pẹ̀lú agbára. Dájúdájú Àwa sì ni Alágbára (tí a mú un tóbi)."
  51,48,"Àti ilẹ̀, A ṣe é ní ìtẹ́. (Àwa sì ni) olùtẹ́-ilẹ̀ sílẹ̀ tó dára."
  52,37,"Tàbí lọ́dọ̀ wọn ni àwọn ilé ọrọ̀ Olúwa rẹ wà? Tàbí àwọn ni olùborí?"
  52,38,"Tàbí wọ́n ní àkàbà kan tí wọ́n ń fi gbọ́rọ̀ (nínú sánmọ̀)? Kí ẹni tí ó ń bá wọn gbọ́ ọ̀rọ̀ mú ẹ̀rí tó yanjú wá?"
  52,39,"Tàbí àwọn ọmọbìnrin ni tiRẹ̀, àwọn ọmọkùnrin sì ni tiyín?"
  53,31,"Ti Allāhu ni ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó wà nínú ilẹ̀ nítorí kí Ó lè san àwọn tó ṣe iṣẹ́ aburú ní ẹ̀san ohun tí wọ́n ṣe níṣẹ́ àti nítorí kí Ó lè san àwọn tó ṣe iṣẹ́ rere ni ẹ̀san rere."
  53,32,"Àwọn tó ń jìnnà sí ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ ńlá ńlá àti ìwà ìbàjẹ́ àyàfi àwọn ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ wẹẹrẹ, dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ gbòòrò ní àforíjìn. Ó nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa yín nígbà tí Ó ṣẹ̀dá yín láti inú ilẹ̀ àti nígbà tí ẹ wà ní ọlẹ̀ nínú àwọn ikùn ìyá yín. Nítorí náà, ẹ má ṣe fọra yín mọ́.{1} Òun l’Ó nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ẹni tó bẹ̀rù (Rẹ̀)..",footnotes:1:Ìyẹn ni pé, ẹ má ṣe yin ara yín.
  53,33,"Sọ fún mi nípa ẹni tó gbúnrí (kúrò níbi òdodo),"
  54,22,"Dájúdájú A ṣe al-Ƙur’ān ní ìrọ̀rùn fún ṣíṣe ìrántí. Ǹjẹ́ olùrántí wà báyìí bí?"
  54,23,"Ìjọ Thamūd pe àwọn ìkìlọ̀ ní irọ́."
  54,24,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ṣé abara kan, ẹnì kan ṣoṣo nínú wa ni a óò máa tẹ̀lé. (Bí ó bá rí bẹ́ẹ̀) nígbà náà dájúdájú àwa ti wà nínú ìṣìnà àti wàhálà."
  55,16,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  55,17,"Olúwa ibùyọ òòrùn méjèèjì àti ibùwọ̀ òòrùn méjèèjì.{1}.",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Mọ‘ārij; 70:40.
  55,18,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  56,7,"ẹ̀yin sì máa jẹ́ oríṣi mẹ́ta.{1}.",footnotes:1:Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra wà fún ìjọ ọ̀tún, Ọgbà Iná sì wá fún ìjọ òsì. Àmọ́, Allāhu - tó ga jùlọ - ṣe àtúnpín ìjọ ọ̀tún sí ìjọ ọ̀tún àti ìjọ aṣíwájú nítorí pé, ìgbádùn ìkíní kejì yàtọ̀ gan-an síra wọn.
  56,8,"Àwọn èrò ọwọ́ ọ̀tún, kí ni (ó máa ti dára tó fún) àwọn èrò ọwọ́ ọ̀tún?"
  56,9,"Àwọn èrò ọwọ́ òsì, kí ni (ó máa ti burú tó fún) àwọn èrò ọwọ́ òsì?"